quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"[Annabai Ibraahiima] maaki: "Ko ho …óum woni fii mon, onon …ďee nelaa…ďe?""
  51,32,"∆Āe mbi'i: "Minen Min nela e yim…ďe bon…ďe …ďen,"
  51,33,"fii yo min ngaccitu e ma…ď…ďe, kaa∆īe iw…óe e loope (ju…óaa…óe),"
  51,34,"maandiniraa…óe ka Joomi maa, fii fantinoo…ďe …ďeen"."
  51,35,"Min njaltini toon kala gooŇč…óin…ďe wonunoo…ďe toon."
  51,36,"Min tawaano ton, si wonaa suudu juul…ďe wo'oturu."
  51,37,"Min ngacci ton Ma'ande, wonan'de …ďen huloo…ďe lepte mu'usuu…óe …óen."
  51,38,"[Min ngacci kadi ma'ande] e Muusaa, tuma nde Min nulunoo mo e Fir'awna, wond'ude e hujja …ďanngu…óo."
  51,39,"Kono o …óuurnodii e semmbe makko, o wi'i [Muusaa]: "Ko bileejo maa feetu…óo"."
  51,40,"Min nanngi mo kaŇčko e koneeli makko …óin, Min bugodii …ďe ka maayo, tawde ko o pelnii…óo."
  51,41,"E 'Adi'en, tuma Min ngurtunoo henndu bonndu ndun e ma…ď…ďe."
  51,42,"ndu accataa hay hu'unde nde ndu arani, si wonaa ndu wa…ótay nde wa ndoondi."
  51,43,"E Samuuda'en kadi, tuma nde …ďe mbi'ananoo : "ndakmitee haa see…óa !""
  51,44,"∆Āe townitanii yamiroore Joomi ma…ď…ďe nden, ha'acaango ngon nanngi …ďe, tawi he…ďe ∆īeewa."
  51,45,"∆Āe mbaawaano daragol (laawoo), …ďe wonaano kadi faabaa…ďe."
  51,46,"Ko noon kadi yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďeen ko adii[…ďe]. ∆Āen ko yim…ďe faasiqii…ďe ngonnoo."
  51,47,"Kammu ngun, Min mahir ngu doole Amen. Pellet, ko Min ya√Ī√Īu…ďe."
  51,48,"Leydi ndin kan, Min mbeertundi. Min mo∆ī∆īii weertu…ďe."
  51,49,"E kala hu'unde, Min tagii noone …ói…ói; mbelajo'o on mbaajitoray."
  51,50,""Awa ndogee kisan fa'ade e Allah. Min, wonan'de on immorde ka makko, ko mi jeertinoowo …ďanngu…óo."
  51,51,"Wota on mba…óidane Allah dewetee…óo goo. Min, wonan'de on immorde ka makko, ko mi jeertinoowo …ďanngu…óo"."